data.description: This is a very well maintained Southside Blonde Brick Rancher with 2 conforming bedrooms on the main level with a possible 3rd bedroom in the basement. This home has so much potiential to be a forever home. Situated in a lovely neighborhood and near many employment centers, schools and shopping centers. This home features decorative ceilings with ceiling fans throughout, can lighting in the living room along with a wood buring fireplace, central air, beautiful hardwood floors and an updated furnace and cedar lined closets. The garage is heated and cooled and the shed is perfect for extra storage. The sprinklers are on a timer and the trex decking patio is nice for entertaining. Oh and don't forget about the huge driveway for additional off the street parking. See this home today!
